.live-status__icon--live {
    position: relative;

    border-radius: 50%;
}
.live-status__icon--live:after {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2px;
    right: 2px;
    bottom: 2px;
    left: 2px;
    display: block;
    background-color: #bb1919;
    border-radius: 50%;
    content: ' ';
    -webkit-animation: pulse 1.7s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1) infinite;

}
